      • updateNode

        public boolean updateNode​(boolean removeChildren)
        Attempts to update this node's representation and contents based on its status and retrieved data from its parent CalcServerNode's requester. Updates for nodes without connected parent interfaces are ignored.

        Any errors occurring during this update will cause this node's requester to die.

        Parameters:
        removeChildren - if true the child nodes of this folder node will be removed and completely replaced; if false the existing nodes will be retained and any missing nodes will be inserted into the appropriate positions.
        See Also:
        getInterface(), CalcServerRequester.getFolderContents(java.lang.String)
